the article, or, more specifically,
one paragraph.
The purpose of this column is
not indiscriminately to criticism
Grinnell athletes and is certainly
not to criticism individual Grinnell
athletes. Its real purpose is to
point out businesses in the Grinnell sports system. The views 1
take are originally surely my
own, but I have found a great majority agree with me.
In my experience with college
baseball and other baseball of
similar culture, it has always
